description:
Talk about the perfect little Brooklyn get away! The neighborhood is EXTREMELY poplar among Airbnb travelers,  
Its a perfect Brooklyn apartment situated only steps away from the train & only 15 minutes away from the city. 
In the middle of historic Bedstuy I'm walking distance from hip coffee shops, bodegas, fresh produce & fish markets, and some really cool restaurants and pubs, Also only a 20 min walk from the new Barclay Arena!
